## 378. Kth Smallest Element in a Sorted Matrix

Binary Search

```java
class Solution {
    public int kthSmallest(int[][] matrix, int k) {
        int n = matrix.length;
        int s = matrix[0][0], e = matrix[n - 1][n - 1];
        int ct = 0;     
        while (s < e) {
            int mid = (e - s) / 2 + s;
            ct = 0;
            int j = n - 1;
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                while (j >= 0 && matrix[i][j] > mid) j--;
                ct += (j + 1);
            }
            
            if (ct >= k) e = mid;
            else s = mid + 1;            
        }
        
        return s;
    }
}
```
